  <summary date="2021-10-26T14:04:13Z" status="Introduced in House">Stop EITC and CTC Seizures Act

This bill prohibits the Department of the Treasury from reducing a taxpayer's tax refund for student loan debt to the extent that such reduction would cause the refund to be less than the sum of the earned income tax credit and the child tax credit.</summary>
